(13, 'rayban_clubround_noir_cuivre_flash', '98.400 OMR', 'uploads/284845c8f1.jpg', 'Acetate,Metal Frames\r\n\r\nImported\r\n\r\nAcetate frame\r\n\r\nGlass lens\r\n\r\nNon-Polarized\r\n\r\n100% UV protection coating\r\n\r\nLens width: 51 millimeters\r\n\r\nBridge: 19 millimeters\r\n\r\nArm: 145 millimeters\r\n\r\n2.5" high\r\n\r\n0.3" wide\r\n\r\nCase included\r\n\r\nLenses are prescription ready (rx-able)\r\n\r\nNew club round shape club master meets round new addition to icons\r\n\r\nImported from USA\r\n\r\nRB4246 Clubround Sunglasses feature an acetate and metal frame and round lenses. The unisex RB4246 Clubround Sunglasses \r\nare marriage of the popular Clubmaster and Round styles and they available in a variety of frame colors and lens \r\ntreatments including polarized, gradient, solid and mirrored. To protect your eyes from harmful UV rays, these\r\nsunglasses include lenses that are coated with 100% UV protection.\r\n\r\nRay-Ban is the world''s most iconic eyewear brand and is a global leader in its sector. Every model in the Ray-Ban \r\ncollection is the product of meticulous, original styling that translates the best of the latest fashion trends into an \r\never-contemporary look for millions of Ray-Ban wearers around the world. From the early Aviator style that emerged in \r\n1937 to the introduction of the classic Wayfarer in 1952, Ray-Ban is a brand that embodies America and adventure, great \r\ncities and wide-open spaces, heroism, individuality, and authenticity. Starting with a silver screen debut in 1961, \r\nRay-Ban sunglasses have appeared throughout hundreds of films and have been a favorite on the Hollywood scene for years, \r\nboth on and off the screen. With timeless and imaginative styles, Ray-Ban consistently blends high-tech design, lenses, \r\nand materials. The collection remains true to its classic heritage while continuously evolving to meet today''s fashion \r\ndemands.\r\n\r\nRay-Ban is the world''s most iconic eyewear brand and is a global leader in its sector. Every model in the \r\nRay-Ban collection is the product of meticulous, original styling that translates the best of the latest fashion trends \r\ninto an ever-contemporary look for millions of Ray-Ban wearers around the world. From the early Aviator style that \r\nemerged in 1937 to the introduction of the classic Wayfarer in 1952, Ray-Ban is a brand that embodies America and \r\nadventure, great cities and wide-open spaces, heroism, individuality, and authenticity. Starting with a silver screen \r\ndebut in 1961, Ray-Ban sunglasses have appeared throughout hundreds of films and have been a favorite on the Hollywood \r\nscene for years, both on and off the screen. With timeless and imaginative styles, Ray-Ban consistently blends high-tech \r\ndesign, lenses, and materials. The collection remains true to its classic heritage while continuously evolving to meet \r\ntoday''s fashion demands.', 0),
(14, 'rayban_cockpit_or_vert_classique', '$153.00', 'uploads/e72df04d98.jpg', '100% Genuine Authentic Ray Ban Cockpit sunglasses in an official Ray Ban colored box & manual\r\nRayBan Sunglass case\r\nRay Ban Cleaning Cloth\r\nThis model of Ray Ban Sunglasses can be made with Prescription lenses to your exact specifications. If you need a single vision (far, near or computer distance) RX version of this Ray-Ban glasses frame, please see our Ray Ban Cockpit RB3362 Prescription sunglasses page for ordering info. If you are looking for Ray-Ban RB3362 with multifocal (lined bifocal or no-line progressive) lenses, please have a look at Ray Ban Prescription RB3362 Progressive Sunglasses and Ray-Ban RB3362 Prescription Bi-focal Sunglasses. For other Prescription Ray Ban Sunglasses please see our RayBan RX Page. We also offer Ray-Ban Prescription Eyeglasses with custom-made Rx lenses.\r\n\r\nAvailable Ray-Ban RB3362 Sunglasses:\r\n\r\nRay Ban RB3362 sunglasses\r\nRay Ban RB3362 prescription sunglasses\r\nRay Ban RB3362 prescription sunglasses with Bifocal lenses\r\nRay-Ban RB3362 prescription sunglasses with Progressive lenses\r\nRay Ban is a Luxottica brand, and all sunglasses, eyeglasses frames, and othereyewear purchased from us, an Authorized US Luxottica RayBan Dealer, are brand new and come with a one-year Ray-Ban / Luxottica warranty from the date of purchase, and in addition you get a piece of mind of our 100% Satisfaction Guarantee from us.', 0),
(15, 'rayban_justin_noir_rougeMirroir', 'R 4 790', 'uploads/efe12d42d5.jpg', 'Features\r\nRB4165 622/6Q 55-16-145\r\nMatte Black / Red Mirror\r\nProtective case included, cases come in a variety of colors.\r\nThe shape and curvature of these sunglasses may need adjustments. Adjustments should only be made by a professional.\r\nBuy with confidence. All of our Ray-Ban''s come straight from the manufacturer.\r\n\r\nOriginal RayBan RB4165 622/6Q Rubber Black/Brown Mirror Orange Size 54 mm Sunglasses.', 0),
